<template>
  <v-data-table
    dense
    :headers="headers"
    :items="list"
    item-key="name"
    class="elevation-1"
  ></v-data-table>
</template>
<script>
  import Vue from 'vue';
  export default {
    data: () => ({
      list:[
id='',
empid='',
name='',
dept=''
      ],
      headers: [
        { text: 'id', value: 'id' },
        { text: 'empid', value: 'empid' },
        { text: 'name', value: 'name' },
        { text: 'dept', value: 'dept' },
     
      ],
    }),
    mounted() {

Vue.axios.get('http://127.0.0.1:40193/readdept')

  .then((resp) => {
    this.list = resp.data;
  })
},
  }
</script>
